des:
Listeners are treated with a dose of daily Black history and insight from the world famous Black History Flashcards by Urban Intellectuals.

Urban Intellectuals creates a series of historical education products designed to write the Black community back into the pages of world history and the hearts and minds of the people. You can learn more on our website at UrbanIntellectuals.com
